The Government's Decisions:
New with a view to increase the revenue of the state through state excise duty
Additional Chief Secretary, Housing Department to submit measures / recommendations.
The Government approves constitution of the following Study Groups / Committees under the Chairmanship of:
It is.
The functions of the aforesaid Committee shall be as follows: -
a) Liquor policy in other states, type of license, excise duty as well as taxes
By studying the best practices / strategies to be followed for collection enhancement.
Suggesting measures.
b) Policy proposed by the Commissioner, State Excise, State of Maharashtra
To make recommendations after considering the issues.
The Committee constituted as aforesaid shall submit its recommendations to the Government within 2 months.
